Sure, here are some examples:

1. *Odvodim* sina u školu svako jutro. (I take my son to school every morning.)
2. Da li ćeš *odvesti* psa kod veterinara danas? (Are you going to take the dog to the vet today?)
3. Prošle nedelje sam *odveo* rođake na aerodrom. (Last week I took my relatives to the airport.)
4. *Odvodite* li decu na ekskurziju sledećeg meseca? (Are you taking the children on a field trip next month?)
5. Oni će *odvesti* svoje bicikle u park. (They will take their bikes to the park.)
6. Da li ćeš mi *odvesti* torbu u sobu? (Will you take my bag to the room for me?)
7. Oni su me *odveli* na predivan izlet u prirodu. (They took me on a wonderful nature trip.)
8. Njegov otac će ga *odvesti* na probnu vožnju ovog vikenda. (His father will take him on a test drive this weekend.)
9. Kada se budeš osećao bolje, *odvešću* te na ručak. (When you feel better, I'll take you out for lunch.)
10. *Odvodimo* svoje goste na obilazak grada večeras. (We're taking our guests on a city tour tonight.)